      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative metric (E_rel) computed at all five operating points with combined experimental and numerical uncertainty; E_rel ≤20% at all points.",
      "rationale": "E_rel computed at all five points: values are 8%, 15%, 23%, 31%, and 19%. Two of five points exceed the 20% threshold. Combined uncertainty bars do not fully explain the discrepancy at the 31% point. Achieved level 2."
