      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent review of simulation setup by qualified analyst not involved in original simulation; checklist-based verification of boundary condition assignment and material properties.",
      "rationale": "No independent review of simulation setup was conducted. A single analyst performed all simulations without checklist verification. Use error remains an unmitigated epistemic gap. Achieved level 1."
    },
    {
