      "acceptanceCriteria": "Systematic evaluation of turbulence model and hemolysis model form uncertainty; alternative model forms compared against experimental data.",
      "rationale": "Only k-ω SST turbulence model used; no comparison with LES or alternative RANS closures. Power-law hemolysis model used without comparison to Giersiepen-Wurzinger or Arora models. Model form uncertainty not quantified. Achieved level 1 against required level 5."
    },
