      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters characterized with probability distributions; sensitivity analysis identifies dominant inputs; Monte Carlo UQ propagates full input uncertainty to NIH output.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ performed over three input parameters (inlet velocity, viscosity, hemolysis model coefficients). Five additional parameters (wall roughness, red blood cell mechanical properties, outlet pressure boundary) treated as deterministic without justification. Achieved level 2 against required level 5."
    },
