    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/cou2-vad-decision-record",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Under the Minimal conformance profile, the credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 credibility factors. Seven factors were assessed with achieved levels below required levels, and six factors were flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps at MRL 5. The team acknowledges that the model does not meet MRL-5 requirements across multiple factors; however, the submission is accepted for record under the Minimal profile pending remediation of discretization error, model form uncertainty, and use-error gaps prior to regulatory submission. The applicable requirements governing absolute hemolysis thresholds and Monte Carlo UQ scope are described in the validation narrative and in the embedded Requirement object (https://uofa.net/synth/req/cou2-hemolysis-threshold-req) but are not formally bound at the package level under this profile.",
